{
  "stem": "11882.4",
  "chunk_idx": 4,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And you will be interested-- I think a rumor went the rounds that I was a psychologist.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And as I said nothing, I puzzled them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The type-- the secretary or the stenographer was-- there were sometimes two or three stenographers-- were busy, and they couldn't quite figure me out.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Once in a while, he would ask me something quietly in English, and I would say something to him or I would say something to him.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I think the rumor had gone around that I was a psychologist.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "They frighten people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't know whether you know that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was very funny because I didn't realize this, and I wasn't a psychologist.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] Who's afraid of a Latin teacher?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, we went-- I had-- you talk about contact with the defendants-- with these defendants of the post-- the big trial and then the 12 succeeding proceedings that were before the US court, a military court-- I had almost constant contact with the defendants, because he was going to the prison many times a week, sometimes with a guest that would be interested or sometimes with someone else that he thought could confront the defendant with something shocking to stir them up, to make them tell it as it was, to get the story of these different people.",
      "word_count": 99
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he was a man of great courage.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "As the documents told it, he made the indictments.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You couldn't-- you couldn't quibble with him.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And many people would even come to him and say, Dr.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Kempner, you don't realize what you're doing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That will cause anti-Semitism.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he'd say, well, what can I do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The evidence says these men were responsible.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Look at this document, he would say.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so he was a most courageous person.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
